messages.content: Our Q1 2025 goals include launching an AI Assistant with a natural language interface for all products and a mobile app for iOS and Android, while also expanding to a new office in Austin, Texas. Additionally, we aim to reach revenue of $3.2 million for the quarter.
What are the key objectives for Q1 2025?

The key objectives for Q1 2025 include launching an AI Assistant with a natural language interface for all products and a mobile app for iOS and Android, as well as expanding to a new office location in Austin, Texas. Additionally, the company aims to achieve revenue of $3.2 million for the quarter.
